==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dearn
<hw>Dearn</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>derne</ets>,
<ets>dyrne</ets>, <ets>dierne</ets>, hidden, secret. Cf.
<er>Derne</er>.]</ety> <def>Secret; lonely; solitary; dreadful.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <au>Shak.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Dearn"ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> <mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dearn</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
